name: SMI Flavor for ReStructure101g
short_description:
Flavor for importing & processing network/systems management information models defined in SNMP SMI or CMIP GDMO files, into the Headway Software's (Re)Structure101g graphical visualization & refactoring tool.

This project depends on a few other open source projects, which are the following:
1. Mibble MIB parser - http://www.mibble.org/.
2. JavaCC as parser generator ( http://javacc.java.net/ ) for GDMO Grammar file ( http://java.net/downloads/javacc/contrib/grammars/gdmo.jj ).
summary: Flavor or add-on for analyzing Net./Sys. Management Information models
